ed="T" n="0838b01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0838b01"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000016334"><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0838002"/>壽州</placeName><placeName>紫金山<anchor xml:id="end0838002"/></placeName></placeName><persName key="A012506">玄宗</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0838b02"/><persName key="A012506">釋玄宗</persName>，姓<name>吳</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012522">永嘉</placeName>人也。少時出塵，氣度寬<lb
ed="T" n="0838b03"/>裕，於本部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/><placeName key="PL000000012502"><placeName>永定山</placeName><placeName>寶壽院</placeName></placeName>依<persName key="A012508">常靜</persName>為師。照<lb
ed="T" n="0838b04"/>得戒已，還諸方遊學，抵<placeName key="PL000000027770">江陵</placeName><persName key="A012507">詞朗<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>門，若<lb
ed="T" n="0838b05"/>真金之就冶焉。決了疑貳，復振錫他行，見<lb
ed="T" n="0838b06"/><placeName key="PL000000016334">紫金山</placeName>悅可自心，留行禪觀。此山先多虎<lb
ed="T" n="0838b07"/>暴，或噬行商，或傷樵子──避<anchor xml:id="beg0838003"/>苛<anchor xml:id="end0838003"/>政者，哭婦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1746"/><lb
ed="T" n="0838b08"/>堪哀。從<persName key="A012506">宗</persName>卜居<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1461"/>，哮㘚絕迹，自邇入山者<lb
ed="T" n="0838b09"/>無憚矣。一日禪徒擁集，見一老父趨及座<lb
ed="T" n="0838b10"/>前，拜跪勤恪。<persName key="A012506">宗</persName>問：「子何人<anchor xml:id="beg0838004"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0838004"/>？」答云：「我本虎<lb
ed="T" n="0838b11"/>也，在此山中食啖眾生。因<ref type="person" target="#A012506">大師</ref>化此，冥迴<lb
ed="T" n="0838b12"/>我心，得脫業軀，已生天道，故來報謝。」折旋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1747"/><lb
ed="T" n="0838b13"/>之頃，了無所見。以<date from-iso="+0767-02-08" key="j20012392001592" to-iso="+0768-01-27"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0838sgsz11"/>大曆<anchor xml:id="end0838sgsz11"/></name>二年</date>囑別門徒，溘<lb
ed="T" n="0838b14"/>然化矣。春秋八十六，<date from-iso="+0767-03-09" key="j20012682001297" to-iso="+0767-04-07">二月</date>入塔，立碑存焉。</p>
